snippet.title: Good Company Trailer 2019
snippet.description:
Good Company is a corporate machinery simulator. Become a hands-on tycoon and forge a global robot-manufacturing corporation. Wishlist on Steam: https://bit.ly/2Gz3cjI

Good Company is still in development. If you want to know more about the game, follow and support us:

http://www.chasing-carrots.com/
